Class CaseExpression<X,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.jdbc.expr.CaseExpression<X,R>
  • Type Parameters:
    X - type of filter
    R - return type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    SQLExpression<R>, SQLValue<R>, Targetted<R>

    public class CaseExpression<X,R>
extends java.lang.Object
implements SQLExpression<R>
    Combines SQLExpressions as a CASE statement. A CASE expression consists of a series of expressions with corresponding SQLFilters for which records they apply to and a default SQLExpression when no filters applu.
